snippet.title: Limb Chopper Steam Trailer 01- #gamedev #indiehorror #horror
snippet.description:
Limb Chopper, a PS1 retro-styled slasher/horror third person shooter, launches on Steam October 1, 2024.  Check out our website for updates, news, wishlisting the game, etc.

Head over to Steam and search for Limb Chopper, as soon as the Store Page publishes, and show your support by wishlisting the game!

Jade Pixel Games Official Website: https://jadepixelgames.com
X: https://x.com/JPixelGames
